    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Deseed your<strong> sweet pointed pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and slice into rings</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
