    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush your<strong> garlic clove[s]</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and remove the skin[s], chop them roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the dish with your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> bay leaf[ves] </strong>and <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p>",
