    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle in your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> and add 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[585ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[765ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for an initial 15 min</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
