    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 15 min, remove the dish from the oven, add your <strong>giant</strong> <strong>couscous</strong> and season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Top with your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong></p>",
