    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the dish to the oven for 10 min further or until the couscous is tender and the fish is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p>",
