      "instruction": "<p>To serve, break the fish up into rough bite-sized pieces and tear your <strong>parsley </strong>and <strong>dill</strong> all over – this is your <strong>one-pot smoky Spanish-style basa & giant couscous stew</strong></p><p>Drizzle with a little<strong> olive oil</strong> and season with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
